wikipedia_page.main: Coningsby Waldo-Sibthorpe (1781–1822) was an English politician.Waldo-Sibthorpe was educated at Louth Grammar School, Westminster School and Corpus Christi College, Oxford. He was Member of Parliament (MP) for Lincoln from 1814 until his death.
